extendedInfo.description: Worried with your unsecured contacts? Secret Phonebook may just be what you've been waiting for!Secret Phonebook is an application which secure your contacts. It lets you make calls, send SMS and email. You can even keep confidential details about them.Got secret photos and videos you don't want others to see? The new Secret Phonebook is not only a Phonebook. Now it has a Gallery too. You can import and take photos and videos that will be hidden from outside the app.Features:* Disguised Icon, Title and Opening Screen* Intercepts incoming SMS and calls from added contacts* Manages Call Logs from added contacts* Keeps a Gallery of controversial Photos and Videos* Can make unrecorded Calls, SMS and Emails* Can keep online Backup of Contacts* Transferable Contacts among different Android phones
